<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.1009733>
    dc:description "FIGURE 4. Representatives of the genus Dioryx from China and Vietnam. A. Dioryx dautzenbergi Páll-Gergely nom. nov., Phi-Mi, Haut Tonkin, leg. Messager (holotype, MNHN-IM- 2000 - 31788). B. Dioryx messageri (Bavay & Dautzenberg, 1900), That-Khé, leg. Messager (holotype, MNHN-IM- 2000 - 31785). C. Dioryx compactus (Bavay & Dautzenberg, 1900), Tonkin, Bac-Kan, leg. Messager (holotype, MNHN-IM- 2000 - 31796). D. Dioryx globuloides Zilch, 1957, Patung, Hupei: China, coll. Möllendorff (lectotype, SMF 39221). E. Dioryx kobeltianus (Moellendorff, 1875), China, Kiukiang, coll. Möllendorff (holotype, SMF 39298). Scales represent 5 mm; upper scale refers to figs A – B, lower scale refers to figs C – E. Photos: M. Caballer Gutierrez (A – C); B. Páll-Gergely (D – E)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/1009733/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

